=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得閒研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2027dbc64e79a475f213b2162a6f635058f16bf4","tid":386600,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打試過做ajax call去controller<br />\n但因為接連同一個ajax call做得太快<br />\ndatabase update果陣入錯咗data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83cefee6962a63f68da27f5c9a756b93101dfec","tid":386600,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打試過做ajax call去controller<br />\n但因為接連同一個ajax call做得太快<br />\ndatabase update果陣入錯咗data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用mongo? postgres呢個年代唔可能發生呢啲事"},{"pid":"61c0cfbfce6f16ec24c2e0c56b4f9e926d026dcc","tid":386600,"uid":9248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"946a8bc6d3b33e126b1e7e5b9fdda0ccb43069de","tid":386600,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打試過做ajax call去controller<br />\n但因為接連同一個ajax call做得太快<br />\ndatabase update果陣入錯咗data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用mongo? postgres呢個年代唔可能發生呢啲事</blockquote><br />\n我用緊postgres<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係唔係因為我用ajax連續又好快咁call緊同一個controller action<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8174894afc196ee5fbfbe3a0d2eda89b082a5cb5","tid":386600,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打試過做ajax call去controller<br />\n但因為接連同一個ajax call做得太快<br />\ndatabase update果陣入錯咗data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用mongo? postgres呢個年代唔可能發生呢啲事</blockquote><br />\n我用緊postgres<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係唔係因為我用ajax連續又好快咁call緊同一個controller action<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔似係DB問題<br />\n你試下update完用callback log番啲data出嚟望望"},{"pid":"5b41d176b97278bd2404a26bdad4e8312ebeeeb1","tid":386600,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打試過做ajax call去controller<br />\n但因為接連同一個ajax call做得太快<br />\ndatabase update果陣入錯咗data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用mongo? postgres呢個年代唔可能發生呢啲事</blockquote><br />\n我用緊postgres<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係唔係因為我用ajax連續又好快咁call緊同一個controller action<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔似係DB問題<br />\n你試下update完用callback log番啲data出嚟望望</blockquote><br />\n我終於知係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當我轉咗某個entry嘅數值<br />\n個list query出嚟嘅次序唔同咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如我有兩個人名：<br />\nPeter<br />\nJohn<br />\n<br />\n當我用ajax mark佢地落database 類似咁：<br />\nPeter 出席<br />\nJohn 缺席<br />\n<br />\n結果reload完個page佢出返：<br />\nJohn 缺席<br />\nPeter 出席<br />\n<br />\n我開頭以為ajax call落錯咗data<br />\n點知原來係個data影響咗query出嚟嘅次序<br />\n我無睇清楚人名以為佢mark調轉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}